Package api.equinix.javasdk.ibxsmartview.model

package api.equinix.javasdk.ibxsmartview.model
IBX SmartView model interfaces for the Equinix Java SDK. Defines data access contracts for sensor readings, power readings, environment data, streaming subscriptions, and other IBX SmartView resources. The SensorReading interface provides access to temperature, humidity, and airflow measurements, while PowerReading covers power circuit data. These read-only models represent point-in-time facility measurements.
